AudioManager.playBgm({"name":"00_Lively_Market","volume":90,"pitch":50,"pan":0})
What did you say-!?\n< Splendour >
I-I-I-I\n< Splendour >

The Brillante family's heirloom has been stolen
again!?\n< Splendour >

Yes. It seems that the merchant brought by the
young lady has... run off with it...\n< Maid Soldier >
What a disaster...\n< Splendour >

We are currently arranging a search party. Please
wait here, young lady.\n< Maid Soldier >
...Understood\n< Splendour >

Yes. Then I will go and discuss this matter,
please excuse me.\n< Maid Soldier >

I cannot just sit idly by. I must reclaim what I
have lost myself...!\n< Splendour >
First, I should head towards the capital.\n< Splendour >
AudioManager.playSe({"name":"Run","volume":100,"pitch":100,"pan":0})

Oh, you mustn't, young lady. You are the master of
this shop!\n< Maid Soldier >
Without you, everything will come to a standstill!\n< Maid Soldier >

Please, absolutely do not rush off to the capital
in a fit of passion!\n< Maid Soldier >

Mmm... Mmmmm... Why do you know what I'm about to
do...\n< Splendour >
Well, I have been watching you all this time.\n< Maid Soldier >
Now, now. Please focus on your work, young lady!\n< Maid Soldier >
Grr...\n< Splendour >
Some years have passed since that incident.\n< Splendour >
I have abandoned my name, my home, and now...\n< Splendour >

In Castellum... no, in the great city of Oratoria,
I live as an ordinary person.\n< Splendour >

Not as a noble, but a different life... There were
uncertainties, but it was a world free from the
shackles of family, a liberated world.\n< Splendour >

At first, due to my unfamiliarity with common
life, I caused various problems, but with the help
of Lady Erika and Lady Cecilia, I now understand
the ways of the common folk.\n< Splendour >
$gameScreen.showPicture(7,"hiroiheya2-event/3人の冒険者",0,0,0,100,100,255,0)

And now, I have renovated the brothel that escaped
damage and am running an adventurers' guild.\n< Splendour >

Perhaps due to my talents, it is thriving every
day.\n< Splendour >

But all of this is thanks to Oratoria... thanks to
my sister.\n< Splendour >

After the monsters disappeared from the streets of
Castellum, my sister immediately volunteered for
the city's reconstruction and dedicated herself to
it.\n< Splendour >

Her achievements were tremendous, and now the city
is larger and more vibrant than before.\n< Splendour >

I hear that even now my sister does not consider
succession and works freely and unrestrained.\n< Splendour >

Unlike father, she boldly claimed to believe in
skills... in people... in individuals over
traditional families and bloodlines.\n< Splendour >

Perhaps because of that, I hear that her personal
assets now far exceed those of Duke Grazia.\n< Splendour >
As expected... my sister is truly remarkable.\n< Splendour >

But is that alright with you? You would earn a
better salary working for the Grazia family,
wouldn't you?\n< Splendour >

Are you saying that again? I wish to serve by your
side forever, young lady.\n< Maid Soldier >

I have been by your side since you were born,
please let me serve you until the end.\n< Maid Soldier >
Mmm... If that is what you wish...\n< Splendour >
My apologies for the foolish question.\n< Splendour >
Yes. Besides, Grazia will...\n< Splendour >

Likely come to an end in the near future. With
both my sister and myself being as we are now.\n< Splendour >

I feel sorry for father, but everything eventually
perishes. Just like past civilizations that have
faded away.\n< Splendour >

...But surely there are things that will never
disappear.\n< Splendour >
We are... human.\n< Splendour >

We fall in love, cherish love, and nurture our
children.\n< Splendour >

The blood ties of family may cease, but feelings
and words will continue to connect us.\n< Splendour >

I must convey it just like Lady Mary... "I like
you"... "I love you".\n< Splendour >
Mommy! Mommy!\n<???>
Ah, what is it? My radiance... and...\n< Splendour >
レナイベント
レナイベント
My daughter, Serena.\n< Splendour >

(She is my daughter, but I have never exchanged
vows with a man.)\n< Splendour >

(Surely, it must be the reincarnation of Lord Tim,
who fell asleep within me that time.)\n< Splendour >

(He left something behind. That's why I gave her
the name I was fond of... the name I once had.)\n< Splendour >
(Yes... Serena.)\n< Splendour >
$gameScreen.showPicture(13,"hiroiheya2-event/セレナとセレナ",0,0,0,100,100,255,0)

(The name I once had is also the name of Lady
Mary's daughter. Hahaha... perhaps one day it
would be good to introduce them.)\n< Splendour >
Erm! A souvenir! A music box!\n< Serena >
Haha... ha. Did you run off somewhere again?\n< Splendour >

Is Lady Cecilia teaching you mischief? Don't
trouble Lady Erika.\n< Splendour >
No...? It's more likely those two are involved...\n< Splendour >
Truly troublesome friends indeed.\n< Splendour >

Don't do anything reckless. This place is peaceful
now, but in the past, it was a very, very
frightening place.\n< Splendour >

Oh, a story from the past! I want to hear it!
Quick, quick! The book! The book!\n< Serena >
Hahaha, you seem to like books just like Lord Tim.\n< Splendour >

Ah, books are good. They nourish the brain. A good
book is like a fine meal.\n< Splendour >
Books are edible!!\n< Serena >
It seems we do get along after all. My daughter.\n< Splendour >
$gameScreen.showPicture(7,"hiroiheya2-event/ティムとセレナ",0,0,0,100,100,255,0)

(I had this exchange with Lord Tim as well... such
nostalgia...)\n< Splendour >

(I have experienced many things. Those experiences
may not always have been good.)\n< Splendour >

(But I believe that they will become good memories
someday.)\n< Splendour >
And sometimes-----\n< Splendour >
We laugh at memories,\n< Splendour >
And move forward.\n< Splendour >

Laughter is indeed life's best companion. These
are the words of my dear friend, Lady Erika.\n< Splendour >

Yes, my journey through life is not over. I will
surely meet another friend with whom I can share
laughter.\n< Splendour >
Yes... like Lady Erika,\n< Splendour >
Lady Cecilia,\n< Splendour >
...and Lord Tim.\n< Splendour >
Mommy! Mommy! The story! The story!\n< Serena >

Oh, forgive me. Now, where shall we start? From
the beginning? Or from where we left off?\n< Splendour >
AudioManager.playSe({"name":"Book2","volume":100,"pitch":100,"pan":0})
...ahem.

A proud noble girl with rare talents but naive to
the ways of the world, which sometimes leads to
trouble.

Thus she makes mistakes, but she overcomes them
and continues to have a strong heart. This is the
story of that girl.
Yes... The name of that story is--------
